data.description: MOVE IN READY! Welcome to Bridge Haven at Citrus Park, where luxury and convenience meet in this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath 1 car townhome. The kitchen is a cook’s dream with a large center island that features stainless steel appliances, shaker cabinets, granite counter top and a large pantry. The open concept to the great room is perfect for entertaining family or guests. The lanai opens to a relaxing pond view. The first floor has tile through out and second floor has carpet. All bedrooms and laundry room are located on the second floor. Master bedroom offers an oversized room with ensuite bathroom and a huge walk-in closet. Master bath has granite counter tops with 2 sinks. Plenty of room for the owners! The secondary bedrooms share a full bath with granite vanity and tub. The utility room is easily located by the bedrooms. Bridge Haven at Citrus Park is a highly sought-after community known for its convenient location and desirable amenities. Centrally located, in the Citrus Park/Westchase area, within minutes away you'll find your local Publix, restaurants, banks, the Citrus Park Town Shopping Center, Citrus Park Plaza, Big Cat Rescue and the Veterans Expressway which leads you to a 15 minute drive to Tampa International Airport. Make an appointment today to see this fabulous townhome.
